{"tid":1468902,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"聯合國出聲明譴責香港警察","createTime":"2019-08-13T23:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T23:37:06.000Z","uid":158888,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5211974acf83439e57640620ead367bd2c369860","tid":1468902,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:02:16.000Z","msg":"遺反人權及國際標準<br />\n政府應該立即調查<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6hlIPYfC7sM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6hlIPYfC7sM&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHUx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=969f352d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6hlIPYfC7sM</a>"},{"pid":"239b4b6c330192a33da62d03329d1cb4421298b8","tid":1468902,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:12:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8eec97aaac916f7c8015bcf4d5bbb3363730266","tid":1468902,"uid":263150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5211974acf83439e57640620ead367bd2c369860","tid":1468902,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:02:16.000Z","msg":"遺反人權及國際標準<br />\n政府應該立即調查<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6hlIPYfC7sM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6hlIPYfC7sM&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHUx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=969f352d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6hlIPYfC7sM</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:12:53.000Z","msg":"又只係譴責、促請⋯<br />\n<br />\n幾時會有實質D嘢⋯"},{"pid":"b5fad62a1916794d3739700e16d49b86dd85ab04","tid":1468902,"uid":78016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:13:08.000Z","msg":"陳雲：中共在機場引誘香港示威者犯錯，破壞我的中場休息的策略。我提議中場休息、暫停武力衝擊，改為文宣與和平展覽，是要定格在星期日晚上香港人的純粹受害人的境地，之後交由國際社會支援香港。<br />\n如果示威者偏偏要破壞我的策略，那我只能任由他們。<span style=\"color: red;\">你們如果在期間逞強而打傷打殘了警察或黑社會，現在援助了香港的外國政客將會很尷尬，往後也不必期待人家放心來聲援你</span>。你等共產黨直接統治吧。<br />\n今晚，特朗普總統用推特宣布中國調兵接近香港邊境，他在製造中共大軍壓境的局面，方便美國介入香港，故此各位必須稍安毋躁，不要輕舉妄動。<br />\n機場的環境，眾目睽睽，三層樓的觀眾在看着你，沒有街角暗巷，你打人的一舉一動都被拍攝和頂證，是中共用苦肉計來引誘示威者動武，彼此泥漿摔角，大家打個和，令到無人佔據道德優勢的好場地。<br />\n我也是那麼一句，你要逞強，可以過羅湖那邊打中共的，毋須留在受到若干殘餘英式法治與國際監護的香港。你留在香港來鬥爭，本身就是一個策略的決定，那麼為什麼你不聰明一點呢？香港建國之後，你要打中共，可以參加軍隊來打。忍耐一下吧。<br />\n<br />\n個人評論:<br />\n香港人宜家係要對國展露慘態<br />\n攞國際道德高地爭取支持<br />\n你宜個時候黎報仇或勇武會前功盡廢<br />\n慢慢國際聲音蘊釀緊 支持香港建國<br />\n請各位三思"},{"pid":"d012c9147f7835ee0e2b8bae621933b35d0cbceb","tid":1468902,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e574531f1d765920f5128b742f80b4e6ab5e81","tid":1468902,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8eec97aaac916f7c8015bcf4d5bbb3363730266","tid":1468902,"uid":263150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5211974acf83439e57640620ead367bd2c369860","tid":1468902,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:02:16.000Z","msg":"遺反人權及國際標準<br />\n政府應該立即調查<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6hlIPYfC7sM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6hlIPYfC7sM&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHUx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=969f352d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6hlIPYfC7sM</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:12:53.000Z","msg":"又只係譴責、促請⋯<br />\n<br />\n幾時會有實質D嘢⋯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:35:08.000Z","msg":"肯出聲明都好好<br />\n我地可以攞嚟做文宣<br />\n可以攞嚟屌政府<br />\n可以去話俾美國知要求加快通過人權法<br />\n可以去TG生產商要求佢地停賣軍火俾警犬"},{"pid":"be67dccfe24fa1a1cfa4e3b86ca83fb416bcb8dc","tid":1468902,"uid":263150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34e574531f1d765920f5128b742f80b4e6ab5e81","tid":1468902,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8eec97aaac916f7c8015bcf4d5bbb3363730266","tid":1468902,"uid":263150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5211974acf83439e57640620ead367bd2c369860","tid":1468902,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:02:16.000Z","msg":"遺反人權